TITLE: Implementing Local Resolvers for @client Fields in JavaScript
DESCRIPTION: This snippet defines local resolvers for the @client isInCart field, showing how to check if an item is in the cart by reading from the cache and performing a calculation.
SOURCE: https://github.com/apollographql/apollo-client/blob/main/docs/source/local-state/local-resolvers.mdx#_snippet_16

LANGUAGE: js
CODE:
```
import { GET_CART_ITEMS } from './pages/cart';

export const resolvers = {
  Launch: {
    isInCart: (launch, _, { cache }) => {
      const { cartItems } = cache.readQuery({ query: GET_CART_ITEMS });
      return cartItems.includes(launch.id);
    },
  },
};
```

