TITLE: Handling server response and modifying data in Apollo Link
DESCRIPTION: This example demonstrates how to process the server's response within a custom Apollo Link by using the observable's `map` method to modify or inspect the response data before passing it back up the link chain.
SOURCE: https://github.com/apollographql/apollo-client/blob/main/docs/source/api/link/introduction.mdx#_snippet_1

LANGUAGE: JavaScript
CODE:
```
// BEFORE (NO INTERACTION)
return forward(operation);

// AFTER
return forward(operation).map((data) => {
  // ...modify result as desired here...
  return data;
});
```

