TITLE: Initializing RetryLink in Apollo Client (JavaScript)
DESCRIPTION: This snippet demonstrates how to import and instantiate the `RetryLink` from the `@apollo/client/link/retry` package. This `RetryLink` is used to automatically retry failed GraphQL operations due to network issues. No specific configuration is done here; it uses the default settings.  The code imports the `RetryLink` and creates a new instance.
SOURCE: https://github.com/apollographql/apollo-client/blob/main/docs/source/api/link/apollo-link-retry.mdx#_snippet_0

LANGUAGE: javascript
CODE:
```
import { RetryLink } from "@apollo/client/link/retry";

const link = new RetryLink();
```

