TITLE: Creating Basic Context Links - Apollo Client - JavaScript
DESCRIPTION: Demonstrates the fundamental usage of the `setContext` link to modify the operation context. It shows examples for setting a static header synchronously and performing an asynchronous operation (simulated with a timeout) to add data to the context using a Promise. The function provided to `setContext` receives the current request and the previous context.
