TITLE: Implementing DogPhoto Component with Polling
DESCRIPTION: This example demonstrates how to use the `pollInterval` option in `useQuery` for polling. The `DogPhoto` component fetches the current breed's image from the server periodically (every 500 milliseconds in this case).  This ensures near real-time synchronization between the client and server for displayImage.
SOURCE: https://github.com/apollographql/apollo-client/blob/main/docs/source/data/queries.mdx#_snippet_4

LANGUAGE: jsx
