TITLE: Configuring Apollo Client with Error Handling in JavaScript
DESCRIPTION: Creates an Apollo Client instance with error handling capability and HTTP connectivity to a GraphQL server. It includes an error link that logs GraphQL and network errors to the console, and an HTTP link that specifies the GraphQL endpoint. The client is configured with a link chain and an in-memory cache.
