TITLE: Start Local Documentation Server (Shell)
DESCRIPTION: Sets the environment variable `DOCS_MODE` to 'local' and runs the `start:local` npm script in the `docs` repository. This script starts a local development server which serves the documentation site, configured to use the documentation data generated from the `apollo-client` repository.
